# VUE + INERTIA PATTERNS

## Component Structure
- All page components in `resources/js/Pages/`
- Reusable components in `resources/js/Components/`
- Use Composition API with `<script setup>`

## Inertia Routing
```php
// Backend (routes/web.php)
Route::get('/users', function () {
    return Inertia::render('Users/Index', [
        'users' => User::all()
    ]);
});
```
```vue
<!-- Frontend (resources/js/Pages/Users/Index.vue) -->
<template>
  <div>
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <div v-for="user in users" :key="user.id">
      {{ user.name }}
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<script setup>
import { ref } from 'vue'

const props = defineProps({
  users: Array
})

const title = ref('Users List')
</script>
```

